summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of Six Hundred ($600.00 ) Dollars out of the general fund of the City of Seattle in settlement of the claim of Olga C. Kuhlmann, for personal injuries received by Olga C. Kuhlmann on the 2nd day of May, 1916, while walking on Angeline Street in front of 3903, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
